static method no need an object to call

public class Main {
  static void method() {
    System.out.println("This is static");
  }

  public static void main(String[ ] args) {
    method(); // Call the static method

  }
}
------------------------------------------------------------------------
For public method need an oject to call
class main{
  public class method() {
    System.out.println("Public Method");
  }
public static void main() {
  main ob = new main();
  ob.method();
  }
}
